<h1 id="overview">Build and manage security<br/>for your mobile applications</h1>

<p>Because digital certificates and Public Key Infrastructure solutions offer the best technologies for securing online financial services, thus contributing to their development and acceptance, we created a family of products that combine innovation and ease-of-use to deploy and manage digital certificates directly in your mobile applications.</p>

<p>As these certificates require a framework to be useful, our software range includes a software development kit (SDK) that enables you to quickly and easily create new financial applications, both native (ObjC and Java) and web (HTML 5). eKeynox leverages digital certificates by creating new uses for new markets.

<h1 id="why">A fresh approach to PKI</h1>

<p>To reduce online fraud as well as to reduce costs and develop new revenue in a legally strict environment, digital certificates and electronic signatures are proven solutions that solve many of the most challenging issues faced by our digital economy. They ensure security for transactions and related electronic documents, both on a technical and legal level by enabling parties to establish enforceable digital proof.</p> 

<p>On the downside, PKI is a complex technology that requires significant expertise. eKeynox solves this dilemma by transforming PKI and making it easy to use.</p>

