<h1 id="ekms">eKeynox Management System</h1>

<% diagram = image_tag("../images/ekeynox_management_system.png", :alt => "ekeynox Management System", :class => "diagram-l", :style => "margin-bottom: 100px") %> 
<%= link_to diagram, "../images/ekeynox_management_system.png", :class => "zoombox" %>

<p>The eKeynox Management System helps you deploy and manage security for your mobile application developed with the eKeynox SDK. With the eKeynox Management System, you can:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Enroll your clients and their mobile application according to various scenarios (i.e. automatic, by batch, or manually).</li>
	<li>Connect different Certification Authorities and define certification profiles for each one.</li>
	<li>Define and test your security policies (PIN code policy, white list, authorized web content, trusted ACs, etc.).</li>
	<li>Deploy your security policies and digital certificates while balancing your server load.</li>
	<li>Monitor your mobile application fleet and handle remote operations such as unblocking PIN codes and performing secure erasing.</li>
</ul>

